Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.92,0:03:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Akagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You rightly removed someone
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me join in
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hunh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He was disqualified for cheating!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.14,0:03:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't agree on any replacements!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.44,0:03:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.44,0:03:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You've come too late
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.09,0:03:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,HOLD ON NOW
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Having both Akagi and Ten completes the East team
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We can smash them BOTH in one go
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.14,0:03:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,can't we, Soga?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.10,0:03:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Only...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to let us designate a new rule
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll approve the substitution
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.14,0:03:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that much agreed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:04:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,10th turn alternate playing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,On the 10th discard you stop playing and switch with your teammate behind you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You might call it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.84,0:04:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,pair cooperative playing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.59,0:04:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A MAHJONG TAG TEAM MATCH
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.49,0:04:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing in this way
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,at this single table 8 men can play one hand
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.94,0:04:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.69,0:04:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Replace the table that kid messed up
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,With this rule
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,For 10 turns each, 8 players surround the table
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's one weak point in our defense
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,it will play havoc with the team
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.84,0:04:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And from the perspective of the West team
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.60,0:05:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no weakness... but me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a laughing stock
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroyuki
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Go lightly
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.69,0:05:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,hunh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.69,0:05:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now you're probably thinking you should try extra hard
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you think that way you've already...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.94,0:05:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,fallen into a trap
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,caught by the west team's strategy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's being tested now
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,among your qualities
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.34,0:05:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,ISN'T your determination to win
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Just simply
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,in a normal way
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.57,0:05:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,play as you always do
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.94,0:05:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep presence of mind
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and don't lose sight of...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.57,0:05:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,yourself
