Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We're under rule that wins beneath Mangan don't count
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.09,0:06:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,so everyone is aiming for a Mangan win or greater
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd think this would make for a spectacular game, but it doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.94,0:06:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,When someone feels their opponent has a big hand
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.79,0:06:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,they just abruptly take a cheap hand
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Red Dragon only
