Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.54,0:06:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(498.667,558)}Of course, Mangan or greater hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.69,0:06:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(562.667,560.667)}they're easy to read based on related yaku
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Additionally, as a Tsumo will decrease a teammate's points as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:06:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,there isn't really much point
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not easy to get a direct hit on the West Team players, either
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.94,0:07:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A closed Chiniisou* is a Haneman win
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.94,0:07:13.66,Default - top - cyan,,0,0,0,,*Chiniisou (清一色) also called chinitsu or  chinichi. Hand is composed of tiles from one suit only
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could work in an Ikkitsuukan* that could go up to a Baiman win
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:18.04,Default - top - cyan,,0,0,0,,*Ikkitsuukan (一気通貫) or more commonly ittsuu (一通) : All tiles 1-9 in one suit. A "Straight"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If they suspect I have a Chiniisou
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,these players won't discard a single Man tile
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Carefully, without attracting attention
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,SILENTLY
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.64,0:07:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,this is IDEAL
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Chii
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Harada's ready to go out.\NA Pin (dots) single suit hand
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.59,0:08:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't possibly discard this
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.99,0:08:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck.\NHe wasn't ready to go out after all
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If not for this 5Pin, I'd have a 5 sided Man wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But for that it would be the best possible tenpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.84,0:09:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He may be Akagi, but tiles that won't pass will simply not pass
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.14,0:09:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end my hesitation...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.14,0:09:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,ruined the Chiniisou
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.74,0:10:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinfu, Iitsu, one dora.\NA Mangan win
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you were held captive by that Chiniisou, you could only see the 5 Pin as "baggage"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.39,0:10:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,After getting a good starting hand you thought it was TOO good
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a tough fight.\NSo be tough
