Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:12:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(536.889,533.555)}We've been at the Mahjong Tag Team Match for 2 and a half hours
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(536.889,533.555)}As I thought, Hiroyuki is the first one they'd try to corner
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He's only got 7,000 points left
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.94,0:12:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If he deals into a Mangan or greater hand
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.49,0:12:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,it's OVER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the result: he's paralyzed into playing defensively
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroyuki alone won't do it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.33,0:12:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Endure long enough to pass the hand to your partner, Akagi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:45.81,small - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(278.667,122)}East Team\NTen: 25000 Hiroyuki: 7000\NAkagi: 25000 Ginji: 21000
