Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:45.81,small - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1128,534)}2nd Game\NEast Hand 2
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.35,0:13:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the telltale signs of a *Kokusi Musou, hunh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.35,0:13:02.08,Default - top - cyan,,0,0,0,,*Kokusi Musou(国士無双) Rare Yakuman valued hand with one end tile from each suit and one of each honor. "The thirteen orphans"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.30,0:13:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That riichi. Like intentionally throwing yourself off a cliff
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.31,0:13:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If he discards a White dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,he's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.10,0:13:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,At one stroke another of the East team eliminated
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kan
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The fourth White Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.85,0:14:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My Kokusi Musou win just vanished
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Christ. This is going nowhere
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.45,0:14:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi. Green Dragon. Three Dora
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A South wind wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy knew to aim for my Kokusi Musou
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:15:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and what's more, he did it with that shitty single tile wait riichi
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Inconceivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he using *Ganpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:12.15,default - cyan,,0,0,0,,{\pos(636.445,72.667)}*Ganpai: (lit: wounded tile) The cheat of marking tiles
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That 7 Pin Kan
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,revealed the 4th White Dragon as dora indicator
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.25,0:15:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and the South Wind I drew
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You HAD to know all of these three things
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,otherwise that style of play isn't possible
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.95,0:15:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,SHIT\NI'll beat that conceited fuck
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If we replace all the tiles it's proof against Ganpai
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.85,0:15:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But that just limits the cheat to one game at a time
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,His uncanny "luck" will just show itself again
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.25,0:15:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to uncover how he's doing it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:44.68,small - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(278.667,122)}East Team\NTen: 25000 Hiroyuki: 7000\NAkagi: 25000 Ginji: 21000
