Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,One tile from a SuuAnKou Tenpai?\N(4 concealed triplets)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.22,0:16:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.87,0:16:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitoitsu\N(all pairs hand)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A 1,600 point Chitoitsu
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.65,0:16:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Clearly he won simply to prevent me completing my SuuAnKou
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But when he revealed his hand I caught a glimpse of something
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,While aiming for chitoitsu he discarded two pairs. Clearly a mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If all the tiles were marked, he ought to have been able to win sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.77,0:16:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that is to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginji's marked tiles ring hollow
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.82,0:16:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be very limited in scope
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end: merely a threat
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All bark, no bite
