Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.12,0:16:56.65,small - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1114.222,541.555)}4th Game\NSouth Hand 1
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.27,0:17:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He played a safe pair
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not how someone who knows my hand through Gampai plays
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.32,0:17:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginji's marked tiles are almost entirely a bluff
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.72,0:18:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He's declaring Riichi NOW?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.72,0:18:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one tile left to draw
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just Harada's "Haitei" draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:17.32,default - cyan,,0,0,0,,{\pos(664,131.333)}Haitei: (lit. sea bottom) The final draw which offers additional points if used to win
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.72,0:18:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kan
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.52,0:18:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And with that this hand is a draw
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.38,0:18:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to see you getting any fucking Riichi Ippatsu Haitei win
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.47,0:18:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,JUST in case
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.27,0:18:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Waiting on a single West wind...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.57,0:18:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright\NJUST WHAT THE FUCK IS GOING ON
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.28,0:18:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a single flaw or mark
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:10.65,small - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(278.667,122)}East Team\NTen: 25000 Hiroyuki: 7000\NAkagi: 25000 Ginji: 21000
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:10.65,small - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(760,122)}West Team\NHarada: 15000 Mitsui: 17000\NSoga: 25000 Akatsu: 25000
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:10.65,small - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1104.889,534.445)}4th Game\NSouth Hand 4
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been 7 hours since we started?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.97,0:19:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Break time
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.34,0:21:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We start again
