Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:06.09,small - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1111.555,532.222)}Game 5\NSouth Hand 2
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.66,0:21:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If I discard the South Wind I've got a pair wait on Red or White dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.46,0:21:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If I Riichi and Tsumo with a Tatehon
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.46,0:22:00.36,default - cyan,,0,0,0,,{\pos(657.778,85.111)}Tatehon: a closed Honiitsu (single suit) hand
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.81,0:22:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,this might go to a SanAnKou with Yakuhai-- a Baiman win
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.72,0:22:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.21,0:22:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,my next draw is a White Dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.21,0:22:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.21,0:22:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.51,0:22:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,With this... a BAIMAN win
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.81,0:22:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a White Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.96,0:22:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm certain on this tile's right side I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.51,0:23:14.21,Default - top,,0,0,0,,Finally I've caught
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.21,0:23:16.21,Default - top,,0,0,0,,Ginji by his tail
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.21,0:23:19.95,Default - top,,0,0,0,,In the end Ginji had only marked 7 tiles
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.06,0:23:22.06,Default - top,,0,0,0,,Merely Honor tiles
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.06,0:23:24.86,Default - top,,0,0,0,,Normally, it's done on the backs of tiles
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.86,0:23:26.86,Default - top,,0,0,0,,But Ginji
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.86,0:23:31.81,Default - top,,0,0,0,,while fiddling with his tiles he smeared them with something
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.81,0:23:35.96,Default - top,,0,0,0,,Most likely from when he did that thing... touching his hair
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.96,0:23:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He had prepared something for that moment
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.91,0:23:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and he smeared it on the FACE of each tile
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.69,0:23:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,such that when the tiles are stacked
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.91,0:23:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll stick up slightly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.81,0:23:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing it to merely 7 tiles
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.21,0:23:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a very simple indicator
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.86,0:23:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And now that defenseless back of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.99,0:24:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll cut it through
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.66,0:24:09.42,Default - top,,0,0,0,,I fucked up
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.76,0:24:17.62,Default - top,,0,0,0,,Agreed
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.26,0:24:24.11,Default - top,,0,0,0,,East Wind, SanAnKou, Chanta, 4 Dora
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.29,0:24:27.29,Default - top,,0,0,0,,A Baiman win
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.56,0:24:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A dealer baiman is 24,000 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.96,0:24:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginji is OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.12,0:24:41.01,Default - top,,0,0,0,,There is no second chance to stab through an enemy's defences
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.01,0:24:44.31,Default - top,,0,0,0,,There is only the first swing of the blade
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.31,0:24:47.06,Default - top,,0,0,0,,Kill with the first cut
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.06,0:24:49.36,Default - top,,0,0,0,,This is how it's done
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.22,0:24:53.62,Default - white - top,,0,0,0,,Asai Ginji: Disqualified
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.24,0:25:08.86,Default - white - top,,0,0,0,,Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.39,0:25:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They're playing damn dirty Mahjong
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.16,0:25:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroyuki's on the edge of a cliff
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.71,0:25:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In the midst of a game I seldom use my head
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.71,0:25:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow CHANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.81,0:25:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,OUR COUNTERATTACK BEGINS
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.66,0:25:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad faggot
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.76,0:25:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU FUUUUUUUUUUUUUU!
